{"tid":2352482,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"重光團隊有冇人出黎回應下？","createTime":"2021-01-04T05:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T10:29:53.000Z","uid":13395,"like":11,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f838907d01701092497a4f2bf4bab1c5fe2fcf0a","tid":2352482,"uid":13395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T05:13:00.000Z","msg":"一個崩都無袋過之餘，啲支出仲係自己倒貼。重光團隊同人食飯會claim 錢，但係我兩袖清風從來無claim任何野，一個崩都無呀！<br />\n<br />\n重光團隊自己都承認全面控制1,600萬，佢地要hold錢、要推BNO，攬炒團隊同我10月已經無奈接受，由佢地。無資源就馬死落地行。<br />\n<br />\n但點L解唔問真正hold錢嘅重光做緊乜，走去屈鳩我有幾千萬洗？更何況，我地無每個月燒幾十萬落lobbying firms推BNO。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2352400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2352400</a>"},{"pid":"4aa8dbe59ec00be2a29f17353985a618c6e272be","tid":2352482,"uid":34469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T05:14:16.000Z","msg":"樓主五毛分化pr黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9976259e8242ce28a1ca4ffd50be62b2c4263e6a","tid":2352482,"uid":13395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4aa8dbe59ec00be2a29f17353985a618c6e272be","tid":2352482,"uid":34469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T05:14:16.000Z","msg":"樓主五毛分化pr黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T05:15:03.000Z","msg":"攬炒巴依家話重光團隊食飯claim錢"},{"pid":"8383c8fb24cc5efbd78a994e77e349b0cae54b11","tid":2352482,"uid":40804,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T05:19:19.000Z","msg":"攬鈔鈀個澄清post勁撚陰毒，表面上屌波台，實際上就陰啲陰啲屌柒班前隊友攞錢唔做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ce6d989d0b41509a869ca1754b6b03899f3667","tid":2352482,"uid":6058,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T05:19:26.000Z","msg":"鬥完一個又一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc5937a1a665e0669d2df57f2f760a7e721fe